    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>&quot;Truly Twinbells would be a boring, regular city... If not for The Mysterious Thief, Forget Me Not.&quot;</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333600/extras/645f5c95c0a82a2ec442ed04e3092f1a.avif?t=1766109043\" width=155 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dazzling phantom thief heists, romantic meetings in the dead of night, and making a name for yourself;<strong> The Mysterious Thief, Forget Me Not</strong> is a mostly linear visual, slice of life girl's love visual novel that features multiple POVs throughout. The story is set in the fictional city of Twinbells, England, and shows how the lives of our four main characters are changed forever when a ballet company — and its treasured jewel — visits the phantom thief-loving city. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3333600/extras/136ad496b7b9568bf808a666606126fa.avif?t=1766109043\" width=216 height=64 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >~80k words (roughly 4+ hours long)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The first chapter as a free demo (~16k words, roughly 1-1 1/2h long minimum)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Point-and-click style exploration mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 CGs and cut-ins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four chapters, centering around each main character and a fifth &quot;Finale&quot; chapter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short epilogue that takes place after the main story, going into more of the romance!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two ladies who slowly fall in love</p></li></ul>",
